ok is it forwarded on the right port if not change it
if your ip is wrong in your portforward go to start, run, type cmd and type ipconfig and change to your computer

if that is all good it may be that your server is running on a different port to your portforward check your server.java search portlistener

serverlistenerPort

and change the port to whatever you want
